Log Cabin Prefab

Made by The Giblets of Jesus


Info

This prefab comes fully optimized and ready for use in any map, the whole structure is func detail'd and the lightmap scales for certain parts have been edited as appropriate.

Additional info

This happens to be the same structure that I used my most recent map, Cs_GhostFarm. It'd been sitting there for a while and I thought I might as well upload for people who might want to use for / get to it a little quicker and easier.

With the prefab file, I also contained a displacement ground at the suggested level for this prefab as well as 3 overlays, so if you copy the whole thing over, be sure to check the overlays for valid brush surfaces. Correct or remove them as you see fit.

If you do decide to use this prefab in one of your maps, I'd like to be credited as appropriate and while not required, it'd be nice to told so I could see how people have used it.
